WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.350 --> 02:49.990
[Episode 21]

02:56.390 --> 02:57.340
Young Lord,

02:57.579 --> 02:59.110
why didn't you tell Chong Zhao

02:59.130 --> 03:00.330
about the forehead mark?

03:00.410 --> 03:02.320
The forehead mark just flashed by.

03:02.340 --> 03:04.110
I didn't see what exactly it was.

03:04.450 --> 03:05.860
We're going back to the Cold Spring Palace tomorrow.

03:05.890 --> 03:07.410
Let's not complicate things.

03:07.640 --> 03:08.720
I understand.

03:08.750 --> 03:09.810
Then, I won't say anything, either.

03:10.140 --> 03:11.770
But, today in the Fox Clan,

03:11.800 --> 03:14.010
you could have killed Bai Shuo.

03:14.030 --> 03:15.270
Why did you go easy on her?

03:15.300 --> 03:16.430
It's not that I went easy on her,

03:16.730 --> 03:17.990
but

03:18.320 --> 03:20.440
I saw her dagger.

03:20.460 --> 03:23.180
It's not the first time you saw that dagger.

03:23.210 --> 03:25.340
But this was the first time

03:25.360 --> 03:27.110
that the dagger looked familiar to me.

03:27.140 --> 03:28.850
I also saw some images.

03:29.680 --> 03:30.680
I always feel

03:30.910 --> 03:33.280
I've seen that dagger before.

03:34.140 --> 03:35.450
What images?

03:41.340 --> 03:42.180
I can't remember.

03:46.490 --> 03:47.490
Young Lord,

03:47.520 --> 03:49.890
you have headaches and see things.

03:49.910 --> 03:51.430
Could you be sick?

03:51.460 --> 03:52.570
See things?

03:53.100 --> 03:54.250
Young Lord, don't worry.

03:54.280 --> 03:55.510
We'll be back at the Cold Spring Palace tomorrow.

03:55.530 --> 03:56.620
I'm going to find Chen Ye.

03:56.650 --> 03:57.840
Although he is bad,

03:57.870 --> 03:59.079
he has a lot of good medicine.

03:59.110 --> 04:00.500
There must be medicine for headaches.

04:00.890 --> 04:01.860
Yes.

04:02.400 --> 04:03.360
Tomorrow,

04:04.930 --> 04:06.760
we're going back to the Cold Spring Palace.

04:25.130 --> 04:27.130
One must remain calm when practicing swordsmanship.

04:31.400 --> 04:33.760
I just want to be stronger

04:34.130 --> 04:36.310
so that I won't be a burden to the people around me.

04:36.560 --> 04:38.630
I caused you to lose your star in Outlanders' City.

04:38.750 --> 04:40.720
Now, I've caused Mu Jiu's death.

04:40.740 --> 04:42.330
It was Mu Jiu's choice.

04:45.260 --> 04:46.730
He didn't do it just for you.

04:47.920 --> 04:48.780
Tian Huo,

04:49.880 --> 04:51.030
about Mu Jiu…

04:51.300 --> 04:52.770
Master Fan, no need to make things hard for yourself.

04:52.909 --> 04:53.909
I understand.

04:54.320 --> 04:56.970
Back then, you lost much of your spiritual power in Rong Xian's realm of resentment

04:57.740 --> 04:59.450
and saved Mu Jiu against fate.

05:00.160 --> 05:01.400
Now, Mu Jiu

05:01.420 --> 05:03.070
sacrificed himself for everyone.

05:03.630 --> 05:04.480
I think

05:05.500 --> 05:06.870
he felt the same

05:07.300 --> 05:09.620
as when you saved him.

05:10.640 --> 05:11.760
He didn't resent

05:12.340 --> 05:13.390
or try to ask for anything in return.

05:14.210 --> 05:15.010
Am I right?

05:17.270 --> 05:19.440
Fate is full of tricks.

05:20.090 --> 05:21.800
I feel sorry that the only one who's beside you

05:21.830 --> 05:23.420
will be this little fox.

05:28.270 --> 05:29.590
Mu Jiu is in my heart

05:30.700 --> 05:32.380
and everyone else's.

05:34.840 --> 05:36.650
I've sent a letter to Jingyou Mountain.

05:36.820 --> 05:38.820
Now， the Emotion Tree is growing vigorously.

05:38.840 --> 05:40.640
The Fox Clan thrives.

05:40.670 --> 05:42.370
They will always remember

05:42.610 --> 05:44.630
it's Mu Jiu who used his life

05:44.830 --> 05:46.830
to pave the future path for them.

05:46.860 --> 05:48.270
What about Master Chang Mei?

05:48.690 --> 05:50.620
She has been stuck guarding the Fox Clan for 1000 years.

05:50.640 --> 05:52.560
Now that the crisis of the Emotion Tree has been lifted,

05:52.590 --> 05:53.740
she could choose to go or stay,

05:54.750 --> 05:55.880
but this time,

05:56.620 --> 05:58.409
she still chose to stay.

06:20.310 --> 06:22.190
All of you

06:22.210 --> 06:23.980
have left yourselves here.

06:23.180 --> 06:26.040
♫Don't linger, don't regret♫

06:24.650 --> 06:26.930
But none of you told me in advance.

06:27.600 --> 06:29.400
♫The last moonlight♫

06:27.770 --> 06:29.720
I'm still angry.

06:30.050 --> 06:31.490
I'll stay in the Fox Clan

06:30.510 --> 06:33.930
♫The water from my hometown flows gently♫

06:31.510 --> 06:33.140
and come to scold you every day

06:33.620 --> 06:35.380
until I'm not mad anymore.

06:35.250 --> 06:37.909
♫Sending me to the distant place♫

06:38.860 --> 06:42.390
♫In this life, at this time♫

06:42.440 --> 06:44.030
Since I had an obsession,

06:43.200 --> 06:46.200
♫I dare not look back♫

06:44.060 --> 06:45.630
a thousand years had passed.

06:46.430 --> 06:49.370
My sister once told me not to return to the Fox Clan

06:47.300 --> 06:50.159
♫Is there the same moonlight♫

06:49.530 --> 06:51.520
and be a free girl.

06:51.720 --> 06:54.690
♫On your path?♫

06:52.080 --> 06:53.320
But in fact,

06:53.350 --> 06:55.480
the real freedom is not just about where you are,

06:55.550 --> 06:58.500
♫I'm walking on a never-ending long road♫

06:55.960 --> 06:57.170
but also about whether your heart is free.

06:58.570 --> 07:00.130
Looking back on this journey,

06:59.200 --> 07:02.380
♫In the vast world, how can I get there?♫

07:00.770 --> 07:02.650
it turns out the one that made me stuck

07:02.790 --> 07:04.460
was myself.

07:03.070 --> 07:04.820
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

07:05.630 --> 07:07.220
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

07:06.330 --> 07:08.670
Before, there was hatred in my heart.

07:07.950 --> 07:10.670
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

07:09.070 --> 07:10.810
I didn't want to stay but I had to.

07:11.750 --> 07:14.500
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

07:12.530 --> 07:14.440
Now the thousand-year matter is finished

07:15.050 --> 07:18.080
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

07:15.310 --> 07:17.140
and all animosity is completely resolved,

07:18.840 --> 07:20.520
I'll stay with you,

07:19.030 --> 07:20.960
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

07:20.540 --> 07:21.460
Okay?

07:21.750 --> 07:23.140
♫Time after time♫

07:24.280 --> 07:28.540
♫Oh, melancholy♫

07:25.800 --> 07:27.190
After Ling Long died

07:27.740 --> 07:30.610
I haven't looked at Jingyou Mountain seriously again.

07:31.210 --> 07:32.770
Now that I look at it,

07:34.090 --> 07:35.550
I found our home so beautiful.

07:39.950 --> 07:43.030
♫Don't linger, don't regret♫

07:42.690 --> 07:43.920
This time,

07:44.010 --> 07:46.730
♫The last moonlight♫

07:44.120 --> 07:46.060
she willingly stays in the Fox Clan

07:46.080 --> 07:47.080
to take care of the Emotion Tree.

07:47.570 --> 07:51.070
♫The water from my hometown flows gently♫

07:47.730 --> 07:48.870
She's not forced,

07:49.310 --> 07:50.510
and there's no resentment in her heart.

07:51.010 --> 07:52.920
She's doing it for what's precious in her heart.

07:52.250 --> 07:55.180
♫Sending me to the distant place♫

07:53.180 --> 07:55.380
Master Chang can let go of her inner conflicts.

07:55.409 --> 07:57.330
I guess Mu Jiu would be happy to know it.

07:55.780 --> 07:59.420
♫In this life, at this time♫

07:57.350 --> 07:58.540
I hope

07:58.890 --> 08:01.050
Mu Jiu's sacrifice is worth it.

08:00.050 --> 08:03.490
♫I dare not look back♫

08:01.290 --> 08:04.170
I hope that not only the Fox Clan and Master Chang Mei can be reborn,

08:04.220 --> 08:07.440
♫Is there the same moonlight♫

08:04.850 --> 08:05.930
but the Weak Water Stone

08:05.960 --> 08:07.680
can also bring you more chances,

08:08.480 --> 08:10.810
instead of making you and Master Fan feel guilty.

08:08.590 --> 08:11.610
♫On your path?♫

08:12.090 --> 08:13.090
This must be

08:14.150 --> 08:15.880
Mu Jiu's wish, too.

08:20.930 --> 08:21.690
Tian Huo.

08:22.870 --> 08:23.870
Thank you.

08:40.760 --> 08:41.570
Come.

08:42.780 --> 08:43.799
Come to a place with me.

09:04.660 --> 09:05.660
But this lady

09:05.690 --> 09:07.420
saved me from chaos just now.

09:07.440 --> 09:08.440
If you want it,

09:08.470 --> 09:09.660
I can think about it.

09:10.890 --> 09:11.680
I'm here

09:11.700 --> 09:13.570
to work for free in the Unbridled Pavilion.

09:13.760 --> 09:14.730
Washing clothes, cooking meals—

09:14.750 --> 09:15.780
I can do anything.

09:15.810 --> 09:17.100
You can just order me around.

09:17.450 --> 09:18.260
Huo,

09:18.540 --> 09:19.910
my feelings for you are real.

09:20.850 --> 09:22.050
If love fills your heart

09:22.070 --> 09:23.200
as you look at me,

09:23.350 --> 09:24.260
then your touch on the Emotion Tree

09:24.290 --> 09:25.810
will make it bloom with flowers.

09:25.830 --> 09:26.950
The world is vast.

09:27.030 --> 09:28.170
It's a long way ahead.

09:29.060 --> 09:29.900
Promise me.

09:30.350 --> 09:31.630
No matter what happens in the future,

09:32.350 --> 09:33.970
just be happy and free

09:34.280 --> 09:35.750
like just now.

09:54.310 --> 09:55.190
Come out.

09:59.480 --> 10:00.610
I...

10:01.800 --> 10:02.970
I just want to

10:03.000 --> 10:04.040
make you happy.

10:04.290 --> 10:05.450
I'm not unhappy.

10:06.250 --> 10:08.180
Mu Jiu left. That's it.

10:08.210 --> 10:09.750
You don't have to do this anymore.

10:10.080 --> 10:10.920
I'm sorry.

10:11.740 --> 10:13.060
I just want to do

10:13.090 --> 10:14.410
what Mu Jiu told me.

10:15.010 --> 10:16.320
What did he tell you to do?

10:16.340 --> 10:18.050
Mu Jiu stopped me in the forest that day.

10:24.500 --> 10:26.230
It's a wide path.

10:26.260 --> 10:27.500
Why do you have to block my way?

10:28.090 --> 10:28.900
Silly Stone.

10:29.420 --> 10:30.610
Promise me something.

10:31.250 --> 10:32.480
If I'm gone one day,

10:32.940 --> 10:34.430
take good care of Huo for me.

10:34.830 --> 10:35.510
Do you hear me?

10:35.530 --> 10:36.530
Of course.

10:38.190 --> 10:38.960
Wait.

10:40.130 --> 10:41.800
What do you mean by "gone"?

10:41.980 --> 10:42.480
Where are you going?

10:42.500 --> 10:43.500
Huo seems

10:44.130 --> 10:45.850
not to care about anything,

10:46.170 --> 10:47.620
but she's actually the most loyal.

10:48.090 --> 10:49.400
She is tough

10:49.430 --> 10:50.440
and strong-willed.

10:53.350 --> 10:54.080
In the future,

10:55.020 --> 10:56.190
be more tolerant of her.

10:58.310 --> 10:59.070
I'm leaving.

11:02.630 --> 11:03.440
I...

11:04.350 --> 11:05.600
I don't want to replace Mu Jiu.

11:05.600 --> 11:06.310
I...

11:06.340 --> 11:08.050
just want to make you happy.

11:08.590 --> 11:09.450
I know

11:09.480 --> 11:11.200
you always keep everything in your heart.

11:12.120 --> 11:13.380
I heard everything you said

11:13.400 --> 11:14.560
to comfort Bai Shuo.

11:14.970 --> 11:16.520
You said you no longer dwell on it,

11:16.540 --> 11:17.960
but I know

11:17.990 --> 11:19.540
you haven't let it go deep inside.

11:21.670 --> 11:22.550
Cang Shan.

11:23.390 --> 11:24.400
Thank you.

11:25.450 --> 11:26.970
I'll walk out of it slowly.

11:43.280 --> 11:45.260
Isn't this your forbidden place?

11:47.510 --> 11:48.580
Follow me.

12:00.150 --> 12:01.890
Those names represent

12:02.340 --> 12:04.280
Master Fan's deceased clan members.

12:13.810 --> 12:14.990
I, Bai Shuo,

12:15.020 --> 12:16.300
greet you.

12:18.550 --> 12:19.550
Do you know…

12:19.700 --> 12:22.270
The last time your Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal flared up,

12:22.480 --> 12:23.840
Tian Huo told me about this.

12:24.200 --> 12:25.870
These are your clan members.

12:27.730 --> 12:29.320
If they were still alive,

12:30.370 --> 12:31.830
they would like you very much.

12:42.550 --> 12:45.280
[Gu Shang]

12:44.190 --> 12:45.460
This is my grandfather.

12:49.780 --> 12:51.020
This is my brother.

12:51.630 --> 12:52.510
Qi Feng.

12:53.910 --> 12:55.220
Everyone says that

12:55.760 --> 12:56.920
the Demon King of the Polar Region

12:57.140 --> 12:58.200
has a mysterious background.

12:58.610 --> 13:00.640
No one knows who I am

13:01.770 --> 13:03.950
or where I came from.

13:05.370 --> 13:06.800
That's because they don't know

13:08.240 --> 13:10.220
that the Baize clan that they thought had been eliminated

13:10.250 --> 13:11.460
has actually not been eliminated.

13:12.340 --> 13:13.640
Baize Clan?

13:16.250 --> 13:18.290
I want to tell you my story.

13:19.110 --> 13:20.070
Is that okay?

13:23.410 --> 13:25.100
If it's too sad,

13:25.380 --> 13:26.670
you can tell me later.

13:26.700 --> 13:27.700
I want to tell you now.

13:29.210 --> 13:30.700
I just want to tell you.

13:32.420 --> 13:33.640
Ten years ago,

13:34.140 --> 13:35.330
I went up the mountain to collect herbs

13:36.510 --> 13:37.990
and fell off the cliff,

13:39.020 --> 13:40.100
but I survived.

13:41.230 --> 13:42.190
However,

13:42.580 --> 13:43.990
I lost my memory.

13:44.850 --> 13:46.570
When I woke up, I found out that

13:48.010 --> 13:50.330
I was the grandson of the Chief of the Baize Clan.

13:51.370 --> 13:52.820
I had a younger brother,

13:53.160 --> 13:56.040
[Qi Feng]

13:53.830 --> 13:54.700
Qi Feng.

13:56.240 --> 13:58.970
Soon, I became a part of this big family again.

14:00.680 --> 14:02.310
Although our life was ordinary,

14:03.540 --> 14:05.470
but it was carefree.

14:06.050 --> 14:07.290
But one day,

14:08.480 --> 14:10.350
the Tiger Clan broke in

14:10.650 --> 14:12.460
and surrounded all the people of the Baize Clan.

14:13.000 --> 14:14.490
They asked Grandfather

14:15.370 --> 14:16.660
for one child.

14:23.020 --> 14:24.660
I'll say it again.

14:24.690 --> 14:27.880
Hand over the child with purple pupils.

14:25.750 --> 14:27.720
[Wang Hu, Demon Race]

14:28.220 --> 14:30.310
All the clan members are here.

14:30.340 --> 14:32.060
Take a look.

14:32.080 --> 14:34.430
There's no child with purple pupils.

14:37.110 --> 14:38.400
Still denying it?

14:41.550 --> 14:43.070
Since you said no,

14:43.100 --> 14:43.860
then,

14:43.880 --> 14:45.030
we'll start killing

14:45.510 --> 14:46.750
until

14:47.050 --> 14:49.000
you are willing to hand him over.

14:49.650 --> 14:50.490
Kill!

15:00.190 --> 15:01.040
Stop!

15:01.060 --> 15:02.020
Stop!

15:04.060 --> 15:05.180
I'll hand him over.

15:05.210 --> 15:06.330
I will.

15:15.990 --> 15:16.880
Grandfather.

15:32.220 --> 15:33.180
Grandfather.

15:33.470 --> 15:34.550
Why?

15:34.810 --> 15:35.600
Qi Feng!

15:36.000 --> 15:36.760
Qi Feng!

15:36.780 --> 15:37.850
Grandfather!

15:37.870 --> 15:39.030
Why?

15:39.060 --> 15:39.940
Qi Feng!

15:40.420 --> 15:41.310
Qi Feng!

15:41.330 --> 15:42.330
Since

15:42.360 --> 15:43.860
the child has been found,

15:44.150 --> 15:45.680
the Baize Clan will be…

15:46.020 --> 15:46.940
killed!

15:50.770 --> 15:52.320
The Tiger Clan found the child,

15:52.460 --> 15:54.270
but they still wanted to kill your whole clan!

15:55.990 --> 15:57.270
How did you

15:58.140 --> 15:59.640
survive back then?

16:00.550 --> 16:01.820
That day,

16:02.270 --> 16:04.470
the Baize Clan was turned into a mountain of corpses and a sea of blood.

16:05.360 --> 16:07.520
The Tiger Clan thought we were all dead,

16:08.590 --> 16:09.960
so they left.

16:41.710 --> 16:43.200
Grandfather!

16:45.330 --> 16:47.060
Grandfather!

16:47.470 --> 16:49.280
Grandfather!

16:47.980 --> 16:51.380
♫Across thousands of miles♫

16:51.060 --> 16:52.310
Grandfather!

16:54.240 --> 16:55.790
Grandfather!

16:56.020 --> 17:00.850
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

16:56.410 --> 16:58.120
Grandfather!

17:03.570 --> 17:10.609
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

17:12.210 --> 17:16.560
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

17:36.160 --> 17:41.980
♫What kind of tree never takes root?♫

17:41.020 --> 17:42.200
Grandfather.

17:43.960 --> 17:44.640
Grandfather.

17:44.480 --> 17:50.230
♫What kind of roots never turn into trees?♫

17:44.660 --> 17:45.610
Grandfather.

17:53.140 --> 17:59.900
♫To break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart♫

17:53.720 --> 17:55.810
Your life

17:56.340 --> 18:00.050
is far more important than you think

18:00.450 --> 18:05.690
♫I'm your wanderer♫

18:01.030 --> 18:02.780
and far more important

18:03.300 --> 18:06.450
than the Baize Clan.

18:06.480 --> 18:07.810
-Grandfather.
-Child.

18:07.830 --> 18:09.550
You must

18:10.020 --> 18:11.670
live…

18:12.490 --> 18:14.320
live on well.

18:17.130 --> 18:18.710
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

18:18.960 --> 18:20.610
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

18:20.880 --> 18:22.990
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

18:21.340 --> 18:22.100
Grandfather!

18:22.130 --> 18:23.290
Grandfather!

18:23.300 --> 18:24.880
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

18:23.310 --> 18:24.020
Grandfather!

18:24.050 --> 18:25.100
Grandfather!

18:25.200 --> 18:26.990
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

18:25.510 --> 18:26.830
Grandfather!

18:26.860 --> 18:28.340
Grandfather!

18:27.260 --> 18:29.270
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

18:29.560 --> 18:31.060
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

18:30.860 --> 18:32.940
Grandfather…

18:31.260 --> 18:33.720
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

18:34.700 --> 18:36.230
I was almost dead.

18:37.130 --> 18:39.540
Grandfather gave me all his spiritual power

18:40.360 --> 18:41.680
and saved my life.

18:42.330 --> 18:43.550
So later,

18:44.570 --> 18:46.550
you forced yourself to cultivate to avenge them.

18:47.580 --> 18:50.290
That's why you got the backlash of the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal.

18:51.500 --> 18:52.370
Yes.

18:53.090 --> 18:54.200
Then, have you…

18:54.920 --> 18:56.150
had your revenge?

18:56.380 --> 18:57.830
When I finally became stronger

18:58.940 --> 19:00.300
and found the Tiger Clan,

19:00.330 --> 19:01.700
the Tiger Clan was already destroyed,

19:02.620 --> 19:04.400
and Qi Feng was nowhere to be found.

19:05.210 --> 19:06.840
I'm afraid he's already dead.

19:07.880 --> 19:09.580
It has been a long time,

19:10.550 --> 19:11.880
but every time I think about it,

19:11.910 --> 19:12.710
I feel...

19:16.560 --> 19:17.630
Fan Yue.

19:19.200 --> 19:20.040
I'm here.

19:27.120 --> 19:28.090
Grandfather.

19:28.760 --> 19:29.620
Qi Feng.

19:30.800 --> 19:32.820
Her name is Bai Shuo. She's the person I like.

19:34.010 --> 19:35.580
I brought her to see you today.

19:35.270 --> 19:40.490
♫If the wind intends to fill the sky with flowers♫

19:39.120 --> 19:40.200
I'm Bai Shuo.

19:40.230 --> 19:41.320
Greetings, Grandfather.

19:41.860 --> 19:42.990
The last time I saw you,

19:42.410 --> 19:48.370
♫The moon's brightness is also the result of stars falling into place♫

19:43.010 --> 19:44.420
I didn't know who you were.

19:45.140 --> 19:45.940
I'm sorry to have offended you.

19:45.960 --> 19:47.240
Please forgive me.

19:49.170 --> 19:50.650
Fan Yue is the person I like.

19:49.650 --> 19:52.590
♫As the wind stirs, the clouds gather♫

19:53.440 --> 19:54.800
Don't worry.

19:53.550 --> 19:57.150
♫As the clouds shift, the moon becomes full♫

19:55.330 --> 19:57.410
From now on, I'll be with him,

19:57.950 --> 20:03.950
♫Love is the hardest thing to understand♫

19:57.980 --> 19:59.130
take care of him,

19:59.420 --> 20:00.580
and protect him.

20:00.870 --> 20:02.170
I won't let him get sick,

20:02.700 --> 20:04.050
get hurt,

20:04.410 --> 20:05.910
or be sad.

20:04.600 --> 20:11.420
♫I'm finally back to where it all started♫

20:06.870 --> 20:08.310
I'll be with him

20:08.840 --> 20:10.160
forever

20:10.350 --> 20:12.390
and ever.

20:12.160 --> 20:18.470
♫All the answers are already explained♫

20:19.680 --> 20:20.920
I brought you here today

20:19.700 --> 20:22.270
♫I'll owe you all of my life♫

20:20.920 --> 20:22.440
to tell you everything about me.

20:22.890 --> 20:24.210
I want you to understand

20:23.060 --> 20:26.010
♫But we're destined to part♫

20:24.240 --> 20:25.720
that I've taken you as my family.

20:26.770 --> 20:28.660
No matter what danger you face in the future,

20:26.950 --> 20:32.900
♫How can I downplay this?♫

20:28.680 --> 20:30.440
I'll face it with you.

20:31.530 --> 20:33.600
So, don't blame yourself for my losing stars.

20:34.680 --> 20:36.670
Losing stars is for our life together.

20:37.330 --> 20:38.680
But if the stars are all gone,

20:39.380 --> 20:40.420
you will die.

20:41.810 --> 20:43.400
Find life through facing death.

20:43.880 --> 20:45.440
Isn't this what you always do?

20:45.880 --> 20:46.910
Fan Yue.

20:47.090 --> 20:48.310
Stop joking.

20:48.600 --> 20:49.850
I'm not.

20:51.600 --> 20:52.880
I want to live with you,

20:53.540 --> 20:54.780
without talking about who owes who

20:55.840 --> 20:57.450
or weighing the pros and cons.

20:58.960 --> 20:59.600
Okay?

21:09.180 --> 21:12.060
♫When you engrave your love into my heart♫

21:12.550 --> 21:15.600
♫When my star falls only for you♫

21:14.690 --> 21:16.160
When the Baize Clan was destroyed,

21:16.500 --> 21:17.940
♫When the heavens fall♫

21:18.370 --> 21:20.170
you lost your most loved ones.

21:18.700 --> 21:23.470
♫I can still connect with you through the waning moon♫

21:21.510 --> 21:24.420
From a young boy to the current Demon King,

21:23.850 --> 21:26.680
♫When my pain blurs my eyes♫

21:26.740 --> 21:29.600
all the people in the world only see your brilliant light,

21:27.290 --> 21:31.240
♫Out of the countless stars, I see only you♫

21:29.910 --> 21:31.560
but they don't know

21:31.890 --> 21:39.630
♫As you turn into a falling star and crash into my heart♫

21:32.230 --> 21:34.650
how much hardship you've been through.

21:35.680 --> 21:36.700
It doesn't matter anymore.

21:38.050 --> 21:39.600
The bitterness and hardship

21:40.400 --> 21:41.670
have all passed.

21:40.560 --> 21:44.130
♫When you engrave your love into my heart♫

21:42.460 --> 21:43.420
No,

21:43.450 --> 21:44.860
they haven't yet.

21:44.690 --> 21:46.980
♫When my star falls only for you♫

21:45.350 --> 21:47.000
If the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal is not resolved,

21:47.450 --> 21:49.040
how can you be safe?

21:47.880 --> 21:49.220
♫When the heavens fall♫

21:49.800 --> 21:54.560
♫I can still connect with you through the waning moon♫

21:50.010 --> 21:51.130
Fan Yue.

21:51.620 --> 21:53.030
I will try my best to become stronger

21:53.540 --> 21:55.210
and gather the Five Contemplations as soon as possible.

21:55.230 --> 21:58.170
♫When my pain blurs my eyes♫

21:56.160 --> 21:58.060
You will live well

21:58.240 --> 21:59.840
as your grandfather wished.

21:58.670 --> 22:02.620
♫Out of the countless stars, I see only you♫

22:03.520 --> 22:07.600
♫As you turn into a falling star♫

22:08.750 --> 22:09.970
Grand Master,

22:10.040 --> 22:11.590
I could have brought back

22:11.610 --> 22:13.780
the Contemplation Stone from the Jingyou Mountain,

22:13.810 --> 22:15.160
but unexpectedly,

22:15.180 --> 22:17.830
Bai Shuo could summon the divine sword from the Outlander King's Ring.

22:18.210 --> 22:19.580
That's why I failed the mission.

22:19.610 --> 22:21.560
If Lord Chong Zhao hadn't saved me,

22:21.590 --> 22:22.660
I

22:22.790 --> 22:24.400
may have been killed already.

22:26.270 --> 22:27.420
You said the defeat of the Outlanders' City

22:27.450 --> 22:29.170
was because Fan Yue

22:29.190 --> 22:30.670
suddenly regained his spiritual power.

22:31.060 --> 22:33.060
Now, you said the failure of the Jingyou Mountain mission

22:33.090 --> 22:34.890
was because Bai Shuo

22:34.910 --> 22:36.510
summoned the divine sword.

22:37.080 --> 22:38.770
You have so many excuses.

22:39.850 --> 22:41.160
But you

22:41.180 --> 22:42.660
only have one life!

22:42.690 --> 22:43.760
What I said

22:43.850 --> 22:44.850
is all true.

22:44.880 --> 22:45.880
I dare not lie.

22:48.170 --> 22:49.050
Master,

22:49.500 --> 22:51.190
what Lady Fu Ling said is true.

22:51.220 --> 22:52.330
The wound on Chong Zhao

22:52.360 --> 22:53.730
was caused by the Outlander King's Sword.

22:53.760 --> 22:55.230
You can check it.

22:55.360 --> 22:56.400
There is the Contemplation Stone

22:56.430 --> 22:57.910
in Bai Shuo's body,

22:57.970 --> 22:59.160
so it's not surprising

22:59.190 --> 23:00.320
that she could control

23:00.340 --> 23:01.600
the power of the divine sword.

23:03.650 --> 23:04.780
On the contrary,

23:05.170 --> 23:06.930
you know Bai Shuo well.

23:07.640 --> 23:09.590
You still can't bring her back.

23:10.510 --> 23:11.350
Grand Master,

23:12.250 --> 23:14.150
the mission of the Fox Clan failed.

23:14.310 --> 23:15.910
I'm willing to be punished alone.

23:16.000 --> 23:17.090
Just please

23:17.110 --> 23:18.650
spare my life

23:18.680 --> 23:20.240
so that I can revenge this sword strike.

23:21.160 --> 23:22.730
One blocked the sword for you

23:22.760 --> 23:24.360
and the other avenged you.

23:24.380 --> 23:25.770
It's really touching.

23:25.830 --> 23:27.470
I just wonder if the friendship

23:27.500 --> 23:28.690
is real

23:29.170 --> 23:30.490
or fake.

23:30.600 --> 23:31.670
What do you want to say?

23:32.050 --> 23:34.220
A few days ago, I went to the Human Race.

23:34.300 --> 23:35.740
Guess who I met.

23:39.090 --> 23:40.690
Jing Lei in Lanling.

23:41.090 --> 23:42.830
Jing Lei led his disciples to patrol,

23:42.850 --> 23:44.700
obviously on guard.

23:44.730 --> 23:46.370
I've never left Cold Spring Palace,

23:46.470 --> 23:47.860
but he could tell that I was from there

23:47.890 --> 23:49.580
just by an evil insect.

23:49.610 --> 23:50.740
Lord Chong Zhao,

23:51.480 --> 23:52.760
do you think

23:52.940 --> 23:54.370
that was a coincidence?

24:01.880 --> 24:03.580
Lanling is responsible for protecting the Human Race.

24:03.610 --> 24:05.480
It's normal for the Eternals to patrol.

24:06.110 --> 24:08.210
Although Lord Chen Ye has never been out of the Cold Spring Palace,

24:08.460 --> 24:10.730
he's been well-known for military craftsmanship.

24:11.220 --> 24:13.250
It's also reasonable that Jing Lei

24:13.330 --> 24:14.760
could tell by the evil insect.

24:15.410 --> 24:16.860
If you are suspicious,

24:16.880 --> 24:18.510
I'm at your disposal.

24:20.800 --> 24:22.080
Whether I'm suspicious

24:22.100 --> 24:23.060
doesn't lie with me,

24:23.090 --> 24:24.200
but with you.

24:25.050 --> 24:25.850
Enough.

24:25.870 --> 24:27.510
I don't want

24:27.540 --> 24:28.860
to see such a…

24:29.490 --> 24:30.490
coincidence again.

24:31.530 --> 24:32.970
You may leave now.

24:32.990 --> 24:34.230
I have something

24:34.260 --> 24:35.240
to talk about with Fu Ling.

24:51.500 --> 24:53.260
Aren't you curious

24:53.290 --> 24:55.150
why Grand Master only kept her?

24:55.610 --> 24:57.540
What place do you take Cold Spring Palace as?

24:57.990 --> 24:59.420
She failed the mission.

24:59.450 --> 25:01.140
Of course, she'll be punished by Grand Master.

25:01.190 --> 25:02.950
Why are you telling me so much?

25:02.980 --> 25:04.490
Whether she's alive or dead

25:04.850 --> 25:06.150
has nothing to do with me.

25:06.570 --> 25:07.890
How heartless.

25:08.490 --> 25:09.690
You're right.

25:09.950 --> 25:11.840
If it weren't for her calculation,

25:11.860 --> 25:13.610
why would you betray the Eternals and become a demon?

25:14.200 --> 25:15.980
In this case, just wait and see.

25:16.110 --> 25:17.590
Look at how pathetic she will be

25:17.610 --> 25:19.690
and how she'll beg for forgiveness.

25:20.500 --> 25:21.220
No.

25:21.790 --> 25:22.980
She never begged for mercy.

25:23.460 --> 25:25.050
If Grand Master gets angry,

25:25.070 --> 25:26.640
she will only suffer more.

25:31.410 --> 25:32.570
I told you.

25:33.340 --> 25:35.230
I don't care about her.

25:43.480 --> 25:44.510
I

25:44.610 --> 25:46.060
left you alone

25:46.580 --> 25:48.380
to give you a chance to talk.

25:49.210 --> 25:50.730
I've finished

25:50.750 --> 25:51.880
what I want to say.

25:52.330 --> 25:53.830
Since you have nothing else to say,

25:53.940 --> 25:55.550
I won't force you.

25:57.660 --> 25:58.380
This

25:58.410 --> 25:59.650
is Heart Devouring Pill.

25:59.670 --> 26:00.840
I give it to you.

26:01.050 --> 26:01.970
Eat it.

26:04.210 --> 26:05.010
What?

26:06.330 --> 26:07.290
You don't like it?

26:11.910 --> 26:14.190
I can forgive you for failing your mission,

26:14.240 --> 26:16.950
but I won't allow you to betray me.

26:17.530 --> 26:18.330
Let me ask you.

26:18.360 --> 26:19.280
Is Chong Zhao

26:19.300 --> 26:21.410
truly loyal to the Cold Spring Palace?

26:21.830 --> 26:23.690
Grand Master, you still don't trust him?

26:24.340 --> 26:26.790
Whether I trust him or not doesn't matter.

26:27.290 --> 26:29.280
Chong Zhao can't stir up much trouble.

26:29.470 --> 26:31.420
What I want is your

26:31.450 --> 26:32.860
absolute loyalty.

26:34.620 --> 26:35.750
Now,

26:35.780 --> 26:37.680
you have started to love someone

26:37.960 --> 26:39.460
and have lost your mind.

26:39.640 --> 26:40.850
One day,

26:40.870 --> 26:42.750
you may betray me.

26:43.890 --> 26:45.580
Instead of waiting for that day,

26:45.820 --> 26:47.020
why not eliminate

26:47.050 --> 26:48.380
the potential threat now?

26:50.260 --> 26:52.200
Grand Master, you saved me, raised me, and taught me.

26:52.230 --> 26:54.230
Everything I have now is given by you, master.

26:54.270 --> 26:55.180
In my heart,

26:55.210 --> 26:56.370
no one is your match.

26:56.390 --> 26:57.190
Fine.

26:58.730 --> 26:59.570
Let it

26:59.600 --> 27:00.430
be one with you.

27:00.850 --> 27:02.300
Then I believe you.

27:35.200 --> 27:36.910
Now, I believe

27:36.930 --> 27:38.440
you won't betray me.

27:39.630 --> 27:40.510
Once

27:40.510 --> 27:41.720
you start taking this pill,

27:41.750 --> 27:42.970
you can't stop it.

27:43.130 --> 27:45.260
If you stop taking it halfway,

27:45.950 --> 27:47.190
the pain

27:47.210 --> 27:48.930
will come every day.

27:48.960 --> 27:50.490
A month after you stop,

27:50.520 --> 27:52.220
you'll succumb to the poison and die.

27:52.740 --> 27:53.570
Remember,

27:53.590 --> 27:55.080
your life

27:55.110 --> 27:56.440
is in my hands.

27:56.910 --> 27:57.840
I

27:57.860 --> 27:59.540
can take it back anytime.

28:00.050 --> 28:01.600
Since you took the blame

28:01.620 --> 28:03.510
for the mistake about the Fox Clan incident,

28:03.590 --> 28:05.330
go to the secret room to receive your punishment.

28:05.930 --> 28:07.290
Thank you…

28:07.480 --> 28:08.770
Grand Master.

28:16.950 --> 28:17.840
This is...

28:18.320 --> 28:19.460
made by

28:19.480 --> 28:20.970
you, Master of Bright Moon?

28:22.110 --> 28:23.380
The last time I cooked

28:23.400 --> 28:24.810
was when I was with the Baize Clan.

28:24.840 --> 28:26.300
After all these years, my skills have grown rusty.

28:26.930 --> 28:27.770
Try it.

28:34.440 --> 28:35.240
Delicious.

28:35.490 --> 28:36.600
The sweetness is just right.

28:36.630 --> 28:37.650
And it is soft.

28:44.930 --> 28:45.720
What's wrong?

28:46.240 --> 28:47.380
In the past,

28:48.180 --> 28:50.710
Xi used to like this kind of cake, too.

28:51.030 --> 28:51.830
Xi?

28:53.240 --> 28:55.130
The sister you've been missing for a long time?

28:56.040 --> 28:57.110
You know her?

28:57.570 --> 28:58.890
Back when I was in the Ning'an City,

28:58.940 --> 29:00.120
I found you suspicious,

29:00.290 --> 29:01.730
so I investigated

29:03.290 --> 29:04.330
about you and your whole family.

29:05.650 --> 29:07.190
Now, you are honest.

29:15.840 --> 29:17.290
This dagger

29:17.320 --> 29:19.320
is a birthday gift from Xi.

29:20.150 --> 29:22.400
Even though I can summon the Outlander King's Sword,

29:23.510 --> 29:26.310
I'll still keep this dagger with me.

29:27.280 --> 29:28.440
I'll keep it all my life.

29:28.660 --> 29:30.030
After she left home,

29:30.060 --> 29:31.510
she's never come back even once?

29:33.170 --> 29:33.930
No.

29:34.540 --> 29:36.800
Xi and I grew up together.

29:36.930 --> 29:38.450
I was like a bully,

29:38.950 --> 29:41.010
but she was virtuous and gentle.

29:41.130 --> 29:42.460
After my mother passed away,

29:43.270 --> 29:45.510
my sister, who is only two years older than me,

29:45.540 --> 29:47.340
took care of me like a mother.

29:51.560 --> 29:53.280
This fabric looks amazing for making clothes.

29:53.300 --> 29:55.250
This is also great for making cloaks.

29:55.280 --> 29:57.040
Yes, it's very beautiful.

29:57.060 --> 29:58.220
So ugly.

30:07.560 --> 30:09.350
One year on the Lantern Festival,

30:09.370 --> 30:10.700
I insisted on going out.

30:11.990 --> 30:13.750
Xi couldn't dissuade me,

30:13.870 --> 30:15.530
so she went to the lantern festival with me.

30:16.540 --> 30:17.800
That night,

30:17.980 --> 30:19.570
we met a demon

30:19.600 --> 30:21.060
and were caught and brought outside the city.

30:21.430 --> 30:23.730
Fortunately, we were saved by the benefactor from the Lunar Hidden Sea.

30:24.680 --> 30:26.010
Not long after we came back,

30:26.080 --> 30:28.130
Xi suddenly fell ill.

30:29.570 --> 30:30.980
It was extremely dangerous.

30:31.000 --> 30:32.110
There was no cure.

30:32.140 --> 30:32.870
Xi.

30:32.890 --> 30:33.960
At that time,

30:33.990 --> 30:35.800
both my father and I were desperate,

30:36.850 --> 30:39.370
until a roaming Taoist passed by Ning'an City

30:39.400 --> 30:40.560
and saved my sister.

30:41.700 --> 30:43.370
That Taoist is highly skilled in medicine.

30:43.400 --> 30:45.220
He said my sister must travel

30:45.290 --> 30:47.610
around the world with him

30:47.660 --> 30:48.990
and recuperate every day to recover fully.

30:50.280 --> 30:52.200
My father had no choice

30:52.220 --> 30:53.740
but to let that Taoist take her away.

30:53.770 --> 30:55.530
Xi!

30:57.290 --> 30:58.360
But after she left,

30:59.020 --> 31:00.880
there has never been news about her.

31:01.360 --> 31:02.560
Xi!

31:02.580 --> 31:04.520
Father seldom talked about Xi,

31:05.370 --> 31:06.610
but I know

31:07.040 --> 31:09.760
he secretly sent people to look for her many times.

31:11.640 --> 31:13.250
If I hadn't been willful,

31:14.500 --> 31:16.540
Xi wouldn't have had to leave home

31:16.560 --> 31:17.880
and disappeared.

31:20.300 --> 31:21.610
You were still young then.

31:22.100 --> 31:23.580
You didn't know what would happen.

31:23.890 --> 31:25.010
It's not your fault.

31:25.340 --> 31:26.470
Can I

31:27.480 --> 31:29.460
see my sister again?

31:33.530 --> 31:34.320
Yes.

31:35.500 --> 31:36.550
Trust me.

31:59.070 --> 32:00.460
Young Lord.

32:01.170 --> 32:02.190
Young Lord.

32:02.220 --> 32:03.500
You knew it was poison.

32:03.520 --> 32:05.060
Why did you still eat it?

32:06.020 --> 32:07.430
If I didn't do it,

32:07.460 --> 32:08.990
the punishment given by Grand Master

32:09.010 --> 32:11.400
would be far more vicious than this poison.

32:11.430 --> 32:12.600
What should we do?

32:13.240 --> 32:14.290
I'll get someone to help you!

32:14.310 --> 32:15.100
No!

32:16.110 --> 32:17.560
No one will help me.

32:17.670 --> 32:19.180
I don't need help, either.

32:19.440 --> 32:20.460
Remember,

32:20.610 --> 32:21.870
in the Cold Spring Palace,

32:22.190 --> 32:23.520
once you beg someone,

32:23.540 --> 32:25.300
you will be judged as weak.

32:25.330 --> 32:27.110
And the fate of the weak

32:27.830 --> 32:29.240
is death.

32:32.690 --> 32:33.410
Young Lord,

32:33.440 --> 32:34.920
I don't want you to die.

32:34.940 --> 32:37.330
I don't want you to live such a miserable life, either.

33:14.110 --> 33:15.520
Why did you come out?

33:15.540 --> 33:17.030
I came out to see

33:17.060 --> 33:18.660
who was working so hard—

33:18.810 --> 33:20.470
practicing swordsmanship in the middle of the night.

33:21.120 --> 33:22.920
Didn't we reach an agreement?

33:22.940 --> 33:25.260
We'll walk together from now on.

33:25.360 --> 33:27.810
I want to be someone who can fight side by side with you.

33:27.840 --> 33:29.120
That's why I can't live

33:29.140 --> 33:30.770
under your protection.

33:30.790 --> 33:32.360
But you can't rush to succeed.

33:32.600 --> 33:33.570
I know.

33:35.050 --> 33:37.080
But after the Fox Clan's love enters my body,

33:37.110 --> 33:38.840
I feel a little different.

33:38.860 --> 33:39.690
How?

33:40.370 --> 33:42.260
I feel that

33:42.280 --> 33:44.720
some kind of power is gradually growing within me.

33:44.750 --> 33:46.260
It's not the external power of the Outlander King's Sword,

33:47.090 --> 33:49.270
but an internal force that grows inside…

33:50.120 --> 33:51.690
I'm not sure what it is.

34:07.440 --> 34:09.050
The Contemplation Stone sucked three Contemplations

34:09.120 --> 34:11.250
and actually generated spiritual power in your body.

34:11.690 --> 34:12.520
Spiritual power?

34:12.540 --> 34:13.679
Concentrate,

34:13.699 --> 34:15.760
transport the power you feel into your energy base,

34:15.989 --> 34:17.570
and then transfer it to the palm.

34:35.750 --> 34:36.929
This is the spiritual power?

34:36.360 --> 34:41.050
♫I'm finally back to where it all started♫

34:37.790 --> 34:39.810
It's my own spiritual power?

34:40.159 --> 34:41.320
Back then in the Demon Race,

34:41.340 --> 34:42.820
you couldn't cultivate the demonic power.

34:42.850 --> 34:44.929
So, I sent you to the Old Turtle to learn.

34:44.000 --> 34:49.239
♫All the answers are already explained♫

34:44.960 --> 34:46.360
But there's one thing

34:46.409 --> 34:47.530
I can teach you.

34:48.179 --> 34:49.100
What?

34:49.570 --> 34:50.920
If you fight with a strong opponent

34:50.940 --> 34:52.150
and your power is weaker than him,

34:51.320 --> 34:54.060
♫I'll owe you all of my life♫

34:52.179 --> 34:53.440
you can use the fastest speed

34:53.530 --> 34:54.360
to strike when least expected

34:54.389 --> 34:55.270
and target his weak spot.

34:54.960 --> 34:57.680
♫But we're destined to part♫

34:55.810 --> 34:57.790
As long as you can catch his only flaw,

34:58.070 --> 34:59.390
one strike will be fatal,

34:58.600 --> 35:03.830
♫How can I downplay this?♫

34:59.410 --> 35:00.720
considered a finishing move.

35:07.940 --> 35:10.820
♫When you engrave your love into my heart♫

35:11.470 --> 35:14.290
♫When my star falls only for you♫

35:15.040 --> 35:16.700
♫When the heavens fall♫

35:16.930 --> 35:22.320
♫I can still connect with you through the waning moon♫

35:22.730 --> 35:25.570
♫When my pain blurs my eyes♫

35:26.360 --> 35:29.990
♫Out of the countless stars, I see only you♫

35:30.740 --> 35:35.960
♫As you turn into a falling star♫

35:38.500 --> 35:40.360
Then, you can survive a desperate situation

35:40.860 --> 35:42.180
and turn defeat into victory.

35:46.670 --> 35:48.610
But what if my opponent is Zhen Yu?

35:48.640 --> 35:49.390
He is the same.

35:54.650 --> 35:56.190
But this is just a move.

35:56.340 --> 35:57.770
He has great demonic power.

35:57.920 --> 35:59.850
Even if I find his opening,

35:59.880 --> 36:01.610
I can't take his life.

36:01.770 --> 36:02.810
But don't forget

36:03.210 --> 36:04.610
you still have the power of the Contemplation Stone.

36:05.040 --> 36:06.070
When you gather all your power

36:06.070 --> 36:07.360
to this move,

36:07.590 --> 36:08.640
not to mention Zhen Yu,

36:09.120 --> 36:10.080
you'll

36:10.100 --> 36:11.570
have a seventy percent chance

36:11.590 --> 36:12.420
to behead even me.

36:13.220 --> 36:14.110
Really?

36:14.450 --> 36:15.820
It's not that easy

36:15.950 --> 36:17.200
for a human to defeat a demon.

36:17.850 --> 36:20.180
But remember your feelings and moves just now

36:20.440 --> 36:21.920
and understand the knack.

36:21.950 --> 36:23.280
As long as you practice hard,

36:23.300 --> 36:24.490
and with the power of the Contemplation Stone,

36:25.140 --> 36:26.180
one day,

36:26.210 --> 36:27.560
even if you are to fight against the Demon King,

36:27.920 --> 36:28.960
you'll still have a chance to win.

36:31.060 --> 36:32.860
You really believe I can do it?

36:39.060 --> 36:42.780
♫We're destined to be together forever from the first sight♫

36:41.820 --> 36:43.030
You've given me

36:43.630 --> 36:45.290
so many surprises already.

36:43.800 --> 36:45.650
♫Goodbye, loneliness♫

36:46.140 --> 36:47.700
I trust you,

36:46.770 --> 36:49.890
♫The one who was slightly late♫

36:47.720 --> 36:49.080
not because of the Contemplation Stone

36:49.250 --> 36:50.600
or the Outlander King's Sword.

36:51.240 --> 36:58.260
♫You came towards me, closer and closer♫

36:51.370 --> 36:53.180
It's because you're good enough to be trusted.

36:58.580 --> 36:59.460
Fan Yue.

36:59.660 --> 37:06.500
♫You enriched my life♫

37:00.210 --> 37:01.150
Thank you.

37:03.130 --> 37:04.080
How will you thank me?

37:10.780 --> 37:14.630
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

37:17.150 --> 37:18.000
A gift?

37:18.070 --> 37:22.210
♫You are the light I yearn for♫

37:23.150 --> 37:27.690
♫You are my determined way home♫

37:25.100 --> 37:25.890
Not enough.

37:28.420 --> 37:33.640
♫Let this moment stay forever♫

37:34.280 --> 37:37.770
♫I'm hugging you in the crowd♫

37:38.490 --> 37:40.490
♫Let's never let go♫

37:41.230 --> 37:46.380
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

37:49.040 --> 37:52.270
♫You are the blueprint of my life♫

37:53.470 --> 37:57.310
♫The morning breeze and morning dew♫

38:04.780 --> 38:06.990
What place do you take Cold Spring Palace as?

38:07.050 --> 38:08.490
She failed the mission.

38:08.570 --> 38:10.610
Of course, she'll be punished by Grand Master.

38:21.780 --> 38:23.390
Chong Zhao! Chong Zhao!

38:23.650 --> 38:24.400
Chong Zhao!

38:24.430 --> 38:26.170
Go and save Young Lord!

38:28.900 --> 38:29.970
Fu Ling?

38:30.270 --> 38:31.420
She was punished by the master.

38:31.440 --> 38:32.990
She's suffering, locked in the secret room.

38:33.010 --> 38:33.830
Ning'an City,

38:33.860 --> 38:34.400
Outlanders' City,

38:34.430 --> 38:35.360
Jingyou Mountain…

38:35.380 --> 38:36.650
Young Lord has saved you and helped you

38:36.680 --> 38:37.550
again and again.

38:37.570 --> 38:38.610
The mission of the Fox Clan failed,

38:38.640 --> 38:40.040
and she also took the blame for you.

38:40.070 --> 38:42.080
She gave you her demonic flower armor,

38:42.110 --> 38:43.160
but you didn't appreciate it at all

38:43.180 --> 38:44.310
and took it off.

38:44.480 --> 38:46.250
Without the demonic flower armor's protection,

38:46.270 --> 38:47.540
the punishment is much more painful for her

38:47.570 --> 38:49.660
than before.

38:49.680 --> 38:50.850
But considering her character,

38:50.870 --> 38:51.990
she won't beg for mercy

38:52.020 --> 38:53.350
even if it hurts very much.

38:53.370 --> 38:54.170
Chong Zhao,

38:54.200 --> 38:56.110
are you really going to sit and watch her die?

38:56.130 --> 38:57.650
She forced me to become a demon.

38:58.220 --> 38:59.460
Now, I'll do

38:59.480 --> 39:00.920
what she wishes.

39:00.950 --> 39:01.810
You...

39:02.290 --> 39:03.590
How do you think

39:03.610 --> 39:04.860
you survived from the master?

39:05.040 --> 39:07.000
That's because Young Lord promised the master that she could

39:07.030 --> 39:08.430
drag you into becoming a demon within a month.

39:08.450 --> 39:09.900
That's how you were saved.

39:09.940 --> 39:12.300
She forced you to save you.

39:13.010 --> 39:14.230
I didn't figure out

39:14.250 --> 39:16.600
why Young Lord had to bear with the sufferings for you.

39:16.700 --> 39:18.300
Now I understand.

39:18.320 --> 39:19.640
It's not about how good you are,

39:19.670 --> 39:21.710
but because she's lived such a hard life since she was little

39:21.730 --> 39:22.690
that she'd take

39:22.720 --> 39:23.880
the little warmth you brought to her

39:23.900 --> 39:25.220
as a treasure.

39:25.250 --> 39:26.850
She knew she would anger the master,

39:26.880 --> 39:28.740
but she still repeatedly threw herself into danger like a moth to a flame.

39:28.770 --> 39:29.600
Chong Zhao,

39:29.620 --> 39:31.630
you are not worthy of Young Lord's love.

39:32.170 --> 39:33.660
I hate you!

39:50.320 --> 39:51.550
Congratulations, Master.

39:51.570 --> 39:53.100
The evil insect has been made.

39:53.130 --> 39:54.250
From now on,

39:54.270 --> 39:55.500
the Eternal and demons

39:55.530 --> 39:57.050
will fear the Cold Spring Palace

39:57.070 --> 39:58.360
and turn pale at the mere mention of the evil insect.

39:58.880 --> 40:00.080
You

40:00.100 --> 40:01.460
sped up the process of making it.

40:01.490 --> 40:02.610
Looks like everything

40:02.630 --> 40:03.900
has been arranged.

40:03.930 --> 40:05.240
Every move I make

40:05.270 --> 40:06.750
can't escape your eyes.

40:07.110 --> 40:08.630
I've been to Ning'an City

40:08.660 --> 40:10.010
and also visited the Unbridled Pavilion.

40:10.540 --> 40:11.710
Only by knowing yourself and your enemy well

40:11.740 --> 40:13.250
can you kill your enemy with one blow.

40:13.970 --> 40:14.820
Master,

40:15.210 --> 40:16.320
I'm here to ask your permission

40:16.700 --> 40:18.330
to send a big gift to Fan Yue

40:18.490 --> 40:20.010
and bring back the Contemplation Stone.

40:21.690 --> 40:23.770
Don't let me down

40:24.100 --> 40:26.130
like Fu Ling did.

40:26.150 --> 40:28.210
I will do my best

40:28.320 --> 40:30.250
to complete the mission.

40:37.210 --> 40:38.000
Tian Huo,

40:38.870 --> 40:40.390
I need you to do something.

40:40.410 --> 40:41.330
Master, please go ahead.

40:42.050 --> 40:43.520
Do you know Bai Xi?

40:43.650 --> 40:45.210
Are you referring to

40:45.230 --> 40:46.180
the eldest daughter of Bai Xun?

40:47.480 --> 40:48.520
Back then,

40:48.550 --> 40:50.570
when you asked me to investigate the Bai family,

40:50.600 --> 40:52.810
I heard something about Bai Xi.

40:52.960 --> 40:54.440
It is said that she left home when she was young

40:54.510 --> 40:55.630
and had no news since.

40:57.620 --> 40:58.570
Master,

40:58.600 --> 41:00.810
do you want to help Bai Shuo find Bai Xi?

41:01.830 --> 41:02.500
Yes.

41:04.730 --> 41:05.690
Why are you laughing?

41:05.930 --> 41:08.220
You were good to Bai Shuo,

41:08.250 --> 41:09.650
but you didn't know it,

41:09.670 --> 41:10.920
or you hid it.

41:11.290 --> 41:12.610
Congratulations, Master.

41:12.630 --> 41:14.750
You finally understand your own feelings

41:14.780 --> 41:16.450
and dare to express them, too.

41:18.610 --> 41:19.730
However,

41:19.750 --> 41:21.830
the Bai family has been looking for Bai Xi for ten years.

41:21.860 --> 41:23.570
I guess Ning'an City and the surrounding cities

41:23.590 --> 41:24.800
have all been searched.

41:24.830 --> 41:26.240
If we want to find Bai Xi,

41:26.270 --> 41:27.830
we should go further.

41:28.180 --> 41:30.120
Maybe the Taoist who took her away

41:30.250 --> 41:31.400
was also a clue.

41:31.900 --> 41:33.380
I'll set off tonight to investigate it.

41:33.410 --> 41:34.380
Tonight?

41:34.650 --> 41:35.730
Why are you so hasty?

41:36.590 --> 41:37.980
It's better to have something to do

41:38.010 --> 41:39.910
than staying in the room alone.

41:40.440 --> 41:41.650
If you have too much idle time,

41:42.290 --> 41:43.700
you tend to think too much.

41:44.890 --> 41:46.920
You'd always think of something

41:47.190 --> 41:48.150
or some people...

41:50.420 --> 41:51.380
Tian Huo.

41:51.410 --> 41:52.890
Don't worry, Master Fan.

41:53.540 --> 41:55.300
Time will cure a lot.

41:55.660 --> 41:57.180
As long as you give me some time,

41:57.950 --> 42:00.280
I will turn back into my old self.

42:00.300 --> 42:02.050
You don't have to force yourself to return to your old self.

42:03.120 --> 42:04.720
To me, you are the best

42:04.740 --> 42:06.220
at any time.

42:22.260 --> 42:24.110
Time can't cure everything.

42:25.190 --> 42:26.500
The only thing that can cure everything

42:27.810 --> 42:28.930
is yourself.

42:39.020 --> 42:40.310
Go back and rest.

42:40.340 --> 42:40.940
Let me do it.

42:41.930 --> 42:43.610
The Demon King knows to care about people, now?

42:46.670 --> 42:48.340
When have I ever not cared about you?

42:54.430 --> 42:55.440
Master?

42:55.650 --> 42:57.010
Why are you here?

42:58.050 --> 42:59.300
If I don't come,

42:59.330 --> 43:00.560
my dear disciple

43:00.590 --> 43:02.990
will be abducted.

43:03.790 --> 43:07.900
♫Writing wishes in the night sky♫

43:03.950 --> 43:04.870
What?

43:05.590 --> 43:06.570
You have a problem?

43:08.020 --> 43:09.660
Don't scare my master.

43:08.570 --> 43:12.490
♫The clouds seal their approval for me♫

43:10.250 --> 43:10.980
Yes.

43:12.340 --> 43:14.040
Not bad, my disciple.

43:13.030 --> 43:16.760
♫You walk towards me slowly♫

43:14.060 --> 43:15.540
The Demon King of the Polar Region,

43:15.590 --> 43:16.430
Master of Bright Moon,

43:16.480 --> 43:17.670
is completely

43:17.670 --> 43:19.630
under your control.

43:17.800 --> 43:20.740
♫Time stops♫

43:22.060 --> 43:26.130
♫The brightest star in the night sky♫

43:22.740 --> 43:24.180
Raise your hands.

43:24.360 --> 43:25.130
What do you want?

43:25.150 --> 43:26.060
What do I want?

43:26.090 --> 43:27.660
Let me feel your pulse

43:26.590 --> 43:30.410
♫Is willing to extinguish for you♫

43:27.680 --> 43:31.110
and see if the Weak Water Stone has cured you.

43:30.970 --> 43:35.070
♫Because the starlight in your eyes♫

43:31.370 --> 43:32.530
Don't worry.

43:32.550 --> 43:34.320
Not only have I recovered,

43:34.350 --> 43:35.310
but I also have the spiritual power.

43:35.330 --> 43:36.210
Spiritual power?

43:35.560 --> 43:39.210
♫Lights up my long night♫

43:38.410 --> 43:39.140
What do you think?

43:39.520 --> 43:40.620
Am I now

43:40.650 --> 43:41.960
pure in spiritual power

43:41.980 --> 43:42.790
with unlimited potential?

43:42.340 --> 43:46.140
♫I'm afraid tomorrow is too far♫

43:43.450 --> 43:45.610
Don't be happy too soon.

43:45.810 --> 43:46.890
As the saying goes,

43:46.510 --> 43:50.320
♫Love you at every moment♫

43:46.910 --> 43:48.590
fortune and disaster go hand in hand.

43:49.000 --> 43:49.810
What do you mean?

43:50.220 --> 43:52.930
Before, every time you were fatally hurt,

43:51.450 --> 43:53.460
♫Don't miss me♫

43:52.960 --> 43:55.440
the Contemplation Stone would automatically activate its divine power

43:53.630 --> 43:58.600
♫I'll always be by your side♫

43:55.460 --> 43:56.830
to protect your life

43:56.860 --> 43:58.490
like a golden bell shield,

43:58.510 --> 44:01.110
but it would also consume your health.

44:00.160 --> 44:03.410
♫I'll fulfill this promise with my life♫

44:01.140 --> 44:02.300
And now,

44:02.320 --> 44:04.670
the Weak Water Stone is protecting you

44:04.740 --> 44:06.930
and also suppressing the Contemplation Stone.

44:04.800 --> 44:08.220
♫Once in a lifetime, forever♫

44:06.960 --> 44:08.330
From now on, your protective shield

44:08.350 --> 44:10.060
will be gone.

44:09.890 --> 44:11.800
♫Every starlight♫

44:10.090 --> 44:11.050
Can I still

44:11.070 --> 44:12.990
use the power of the Contemplation Stone?

44:12.770 --> 44:16.850
♫Is a kiss from me to you♫

44:13.020 --> 44:13.980
Yes,

44:14.030 --> 44:15.960
but it's just that it can't protect you.

44:15.980 --> 44:17.880
If you encounter another fatal danger,

44:17.910 --> 44:20.970
you have to solve it on your own.

44:22.050 --> 44:24.180
I thought it was something big.

44:25.530 --> 44:27.780
It's good enough to have the power of the Contemplation Stone.

44:27.800 --> 44:29.690
I never counted on it to be able to protect me forever.

44:29.860 --> 44:30.620
Don't worry.

44:31.160 --> 44:32.900
I won't let her get hurt.

44:33.160 --> 44:34.350
I'm relieved

44:34.370 --> 44:35.820
to hear that.

44:35.920 --> 44:39.050
♫I'll fulfill this promise with my life♫

44:39.190 --> 44:40.370
My dear disciple,

44:40.390 --> 44:42.870
these are the pills I made recently.

44:40.900 --> 44:44.060
♫Once in a lifetime, forever♫

44:42.900 --> 44:44.460
I've taken them all here for you.

44:44.480 --> 44:45.040
Remember,

44:45.070 --> 44:46.980
take some whenever you can.

44:45.480 --> 44:47.370
♫Every starlight♫

44:47.010 --> 44:47.900
Don't be too stingy.

44:47.730 --> 44:52.010
♫Is a kiss from me to you♫

44:47.920 --> 44:49.550
I'll save more for you in the future.

44:49.810 --> 44:50.930
Master.

44:52.790 --> 44:54.850
It's not easy for me

44:54.870 --> 44:55.910
to sneak out of Lanling.

44:55.940 --> 44:56.870
I have to go back.

44:56.930 --> 44:57.570
Remember,

44:57.600 --> 44:59.000
take good care of yourself.

44:59.310 --> 45:00.760
Take good care of her.

45:06.290 --> 45:06.960
Contemplation Stone…

45:06.960 --> 45:08.320
I know what you want to say.

45:09.710 --> 45:10.590
Don't worry.

45:11.300 --> 45:13.270
I didn't have the protection of the Contemplation Stone,

45:13.300 --> 45:15.220
but I grew up well until I was over 20.

45:15.620 --> 45:16.900
It will be the same in the future.

45:17.880 --> 45:19.570
I want to be with you

45:19.600 --> 45:20.830
forever

45:20.920 --> 45:21.840
and ever.
